api_list.name: Resolve AWS captcha (url)
api_list.description: This endpoint expects a base64 encoded image of AWS captcha (or its URL) and solves it. Accuracy is 85%.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://aws-captcha-solver.p.rapidapi.com/prod/solve-aws-captcha"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "aws-captcha-solver.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
